      <div class="seperator"></div>
      <p>
        As part of the refurbishment, we have added unique dormitory rooms with fully-partitioned bunk beds to enable budget travelers to travel in style, enjoying maximum comfort and privacy. Wi-Fi and private parking are complimentary for your convenience. MÃ©moires de Saigon has been welcoming guests since 2015. We are rated 8+ by our guests in most travel forums, especially on key qualities such as location, service and cleanliness.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row rooms grid">
    <% @rooms.each do |room| %>
      <%= render 'pages/room', room: room %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

</div>
